race.description: Sweeney Estate Agents Country Cup Final Hcp (Bm80)
race.comment: Competitive race. CAPPER THIRTYNINE (4) is racing very well and finds a suitable race. He's been narrowly beaten in fourth at his past couple, beaten under a length in a strongly run race at Flemington last time out. He lands in a good spot from the barrier and will take running down. PRINCESS QUE (5) was solid last time at Flemington behind CAPPER THIRTYNINE down the straight but had been going even better prior. Second to La Fracas around here two back is excellent form and Lane sticks with her. FLYER (14) was much better at big odds in G3 company last time and has to be included off that run while MYTEMPTATION (2) ran well fresh and is better placed out to 1200m from a good draw.
